channel.title: Need Delta 317 Source
channel.description:
Okay first of all I've been looking all day on multiple websites, including this one obviously, using the search bar on each of them.
I cannot find a good 317 Delta source, I've found plenty of posts about good sources/clients, but EVERY SINGLE DOWNLOAD LINK IS BROKE.
Swear to god.
every.
link.
Maybe I'm just picky, I'm sure there's some out there, but I can't seem to find them, also don't say this is against the rules, because 1.) I don't care at this point and 2.) How else am I supposed to request something. I'm looking for something like OverloadX or Roat Pkz but Delta based. Or something like king isle.
All I want it to have a is very good combat system, old HP bar and regular hits, working gs stances and spec, and dragon claw with correct GFX and spec
